{
  "text": "The matrix of the Poisson brackets of the above 28 constraints is seen to be nonsingular implying that the corresponding set of constraints is second-class. Now following the Dirac quantization procedure in the Hamiltonian formulation, the nonvanishing ELCWST CR's of the theory under the gauge-fixing \uf068 \uf03d \uf0bb are obtained as [CITATION_1] :",
